Invocation Name: holmdel school
des:
Holmdel's Elementary and Middle schools operate on 6 and 4 day schedules, respectively to allow specials (Foreign Language, Physical Education, Art, Music, etc.) to rotate days throughout the year. To help students remember the upcoming schedule day, so they don't forget books, gym clothes, etc., this skill retrieves the schedule day from the websites that host the information.

This skill is not affiliated with the Holmdel School District.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
